<item>
            <title>[PIG-1152] bincond operator throws parser error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1152</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bincond operator throws parser error when true condition contains a constant bag with 1 tuple containing a single field of int type with -ve value. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the script to reproduce the issue&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = load &apos;A&apos; as (s: chararray, x: int, y: int);&lt;br/&gt;
B = group A by s;&lt;br/&gt;
C = foreach B generate group, flatten(((COUNT(A) &amp;lt; 1L) ? &lt;/p&gt;
{(-1)}
&lt;p&gt; : A.x));&lt;br/&gt;
dump C;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12443336">PIG-1152</key>
